{"tid":1288473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"注意被騎劫 光復屯門 主谷 及其channel","createTime":"2019-07-05T15:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T07:09:18.000Z","uid":255497,"like":167,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"f3e8addbfa1ca41f49ab5416dd16a77037e05a0d","tid":1288473,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T15:52:45.000Z","msg":"光復屯門主谷<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JbG4XFktS3B8ycpTOHR47Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJbG4XFktS3B8ycpTOHR47Q&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=7b4f4af1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JbG4XFktS3B8ycpTOHR47Q</a><br />\n<br />\nChannel:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TuenMunParkHCG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTuenMunParkHCG&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=754d4453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TuenMunParkHCG</a><br />\n<br />\n由於主谷訊息流量十分之大 <br />\n<br />\n所以聽日遊行人士請留意channel 之廣播<br />\n<br />\n接收發起人之訊息<br />\n<br />\n如遇政黨騎劫，可以如此反應<br />\n1. 屯門公園衛生關注組Fb會有聲明<br />\n　<br />\n2. 遊行當日，起步前講明無任何政黨參與過，謝絕騎劫，就係因為多年來議員庸碌無能，街坊先會自發上街，並強烈譴責任何騎劫舉動可恥。<br />\n　<br />\n3. 遊行會叫有關議員不做野的口號：<br />\n議員無能　自發遊行<br />\n街坊齊協　拒絕騎劫<br />\n<br />\n4. 如真有議員咁無恥想行頭，請各位街坊協助聲援：「議員無能　自發遊行　街坊齊協　拒絕騎劫  」，必要時可作支援學生加油站式包圍該議員，但不要使用武力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因明天遊行眾多跨立場人士參與<br />\n而本活動是屬民生地區性質<br />\n如各政黨或組織人士參與遊行 <br />\n如該人士是以個人身分<br />\n屯門居民身分參與 <br />\n無任歡迎<br />\n希望大家互相尊重<br />\n大家都是屯門人<br />\n為屯門好 槍口請對外"},{"pid":"645d22f55cdb63fc536491669637e421fced0de0","tid":1288473,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T15:52:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"15200f103e07b7e779d08cb368be08ea5a4ec0b3","tid":1288473,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T15:53:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a5e374e4c8dfac528ccb96ebf8786b45b50dce00","tid":1288473,"uid":255497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite